trans-unit.source: The TrustRelationshipInformation class contains information for a trust relationship between a pair of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: A classe TrustRelationshipInformation contém informações para uma relação de confiança entre um par de <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the name of the source <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome da fonte de <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objetos para essa relação de confiança.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the source <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém o nome da fonte de <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objetos para essa relação de confiança.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the name of the target <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o nome do destino <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objetos para essa relação de confiança.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the target <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects for this trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Uma cadeia de caracteres que contém o nome do destino <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objetos para essa relação de confiança.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection"></xref> objects for this trust relationship relative to the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects that created the trust.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection"> </xref> objetos para essa confiança relação relativa ao <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objetos que criou a relação de confiança.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection"></xref> value for this trust relationship relative to the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"></xref> or <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"></xref> objects that created the trust.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustDirection"> </xref> valor para essa relação de confiança relativo a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Domain"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.Forest"> </xref> objetos que criou a relação de confiança.

trans-unit.source: Obtains the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType"></xref> object of the trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType"> </xref> objeto da relação de confiança.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType"></xref> value that represents the type of the trust relationship.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.TrustType"> </xref> valor que representa o tipo de relação de confiança.
